#: ../../content/submitsms/submitsms.rst:2
msgid "9. Submitting data: SMS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/submitsms/submitsms.rst:4
msgid "Forms can also be submitted via SMS. Any mobile phone with SMS capability and access to a cellular network can be used to submit data to ELMO."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/submitsms/submitsms.rst:8
msgid "Given the space limitations of texts, SMS-based forms are most powerful when designed carefully. Certain types of questionnaires, such as qualitative ones with long-text answers, are usually not a good fit. However, SMS form submission allows the easy aggregations of large amounts of data across distances without good mobile or internet coverage. It also can be cheaper per observer, and may suit certain monitoring and evaluation purposes, quantitative inquiries, or simple surveys."
msgstr ""

