msgstr ""

#: ../../content/submitsms/submitsms.rst:97
msgid "Ideally, authentication codes should never be written down. Users should memorize their codes. If a user forgets their code, an administrator should generate a new one for them."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/submitsms/submitsms.rst:101
msgid "Activating SMS authentication adds extra security to ELMO by ensuring that the registered phone number and the authentication code belong to the same user. All SMS submissions that do not meet both these conditions are rejected."
